contentrichtext.text: '''Yellow House''' can refer to the: *[[Yellow House (album)|''Yellow House'' (album)]], the second LP from Brooklyn band Grizzly Bear *[[The Yellow House (painting)|''The Yellow House'' (painting)]], van Gogh painting of house where 19th century artists Vincent van Gogh and Paul Gauguin lived *[[Yellow House Artist Collective]], Sydney, Australia *[[Yellow House Canyon]], a scenic canyon in West Texas *[[Yellow House Draw]], a dry watercourse that extends across the Llano Estacado of West Texas *[[Yellow House, Subotica]], a [[Monuments of Culture of Great Importance]] in [[Serbia]] *[[Yellow House, Pennsylvania]], a town in the [[Delaware Valley]] of [[Pennsylvania]] *[[Yellow House Pub (Dublin)]] *The "Yellow house" in Albania, [[Kosovo organ theft|involved in the alleged organ theft of ethnic Serbs]] during the Kosovo War *[[The Yellow House (film)|Yellow House]] is an Algerian film by [[Amor Hakkar]] {{disambiguation}}
